47:03.000 --> 47:11.000
The liquidation balance is used at the time of liquidation, but there are also several types of balance.

47:11.000 --> 47:21.000
The first balance is at the beginning of liquidation, then the intermediate balance, after some calculations with the creditors,

47:21.000 --> 47:30.000
and the final balance is at the time of liquidation.

47:30.000 --> 47:39.000
The liquidation balance is used at the time of reorganization of the enterprise.

47:39.000 --> 47:49.000
It can be divided into several small enterprises, or some of them can be joined.

47:49.000 --> 48:00.000
In addition to the classification by date of composition, there are also several signs of balance.

48:00.000 --> 48:05.000
The source of the balance is possible.

48:05.000 --> 48:08.000
For example, the inventory, book, general balance.

48:08.000 --> 48:15.000
If the balance is made after the inventory, then the balance is the inventory balance.

48:15.000 --> 48:19.000
The next sign of classification is the volume of information.

48:19.000 --> 48:22.000
