48:22.000 --> 48:30.000
For small enterprises that are not part of a group of companies, it is a single balance.

48:30.000 --> 48:39.000
Composite, consolidated balances are made for a group of enterprises or for ministries.

48:39.000 --> 48:46.000
The balance can be based on the main activity or non-main activity.

48:46.000 --> 48:53.000
The main activity of an enterprise is not the main activity of one of its units.

48:53.000 --> 48:59.000
Let's say, an enterprise has a recreation base on the balance.

48:59.000 --> 49:06.000
You can make a balance based on non-main activity on this recreation base.

49:06.000 --> 49:14.000
The balance can be independent or separate based on the method of cleaning.

49:14.000 --> 49:16.000
There are no balances.

