51:05.000 --> 51:15.000
I said that the most popular forms are the first accounting balance and the second account for profits and losses.

51:15.000 --> 51:20.000
These are the forms that are of interest to all users of accounting.

51:20.000 --> 51:29.000
In addition, these are two forms that are made up of intermediate accounting, both the final and the intermediate.

51:29.000 --> 51:38.000
It is allowed not to make up the rest of the accounting forms quarterly and monthly.

51:38.000 --> 51:42.000
These are the forms for annual accounting.

51:42.000 --> 51:46.000
So, form number one is the accounting balance.

51:46.000 --> 51:53.000
The balance includes and groups the economic funds of the organization in terms of types and placement,

51:53.000 --> 52:02.000
the sources of the formation and the purpose of the organization, and the money meter for a certain date.

52:02.000 --> 52:09.000
I would like to draw your attention to the fact that the accounting balances are made up for a certain date.

52:09.000 --> 52:16.000
