52:16.000 --> 52:25.000
You can choose any other date in your organization and make up the intermediate accounting, for example, for April 15.

52:25.000 --> 52:32.000
This is if you need it for analytical purposes.

52:32.000 --> 52:39.000
The criterion of the significance of the balance articles can be determined in percents from the balance currency.

52:40.000 --> 52:47.000
It is static information and gives only a list of assets and passives of the company.

52:47.000 --> 52:53.000
I would like to explain what is the significance of the balance currency in percents.

52:53.000 --> 53:03.000
Let's say you have money in the organization's cash register at the end of the year, which is only 100 rubles.

53:03.000 --> 53:12.000
And the balance currency is in thousands of rubles, that is, about 30,000 rubles.

53:12.000 --> 53:20.000
Your 100 rubles to 30,000 is a very low share.

