54:48.000 --> 54:55.000
The next form, form number 4, is the report on the movement of money.

54:55.000 --> 55:05.000
This report shows the flow of money, their income and expenses as a result of several types of organization activities.

55:05.000 --> 55:09.000
There are usually three types of organizations' activities.

55:09.000 --> 55:15.000
They distinguish between the current activity, investment activity and financial activity.

55:15.000 --> 55:21.000
This report is also made during the accounting period, in conjunction with the remains of money,

